Question 8)..Two numbers are entered by the user, x and n. Write a function to find the value of one number raised to the power of another i.e. xn.

SOLUTION:

class Main {
  public static void main(String[] args) {

    int base = 3, exponent = 4;

    long result = 1;

    for (; exponent != 0; --exponent) {
      result *= base;
    }

    System.out.println("Answer = " + result);
  }
}
